data.name: customSqlQuery2.Sql
data.value: select distinct *, (select x.Variant from Variants x where x.Id=a.VarianId) as Varian, (select x.ModelName from Models x where x.Id=(select ModelId from Variants y where y.Id=a.VarianId)) as Model, (select ModelId from Variants y where y.Id=a.VarianId) as ModelId from jobcard a left join (select JobCardId,AssemblySectionName from mercedesdb..JobCardDetail)b on a.Id=b.JobCardId left join (select img,PackingMonth as pm,ModelId as MoId,VarianId as VarId from mercedesdb..JobCardImg)c on a.PackingMonth=c.pm and c.MoId=(select ModelId from Variants y where y.Id=a.VarianId) and c.VarId=a.VarianId where fdokno=@FDokProdNo order by b.AssemblySectionName
